ic/user/l/000/83/53/835307.jpg?r=1743756543&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/835307\" class=\"l\">魔法使伊利亚斯</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars1\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2026-2-6 22:05</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">个人玩过最屎的gal，别的gal最多只是无聊，只有这个让我全程犯恶心。喜欢这玩意的一辈子有了</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_47744344\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"765144\">\n<a href=\"/user/765144\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/76/51/765144.jpg?r=1679913536&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/765144\" class=\"l\">白州兔子</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars4\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2026-2-6 01:28</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">实在说，这部作品其实噱头大于本身剧本价值（\r\n而且一个不留神就BE，选项也很反直觉（比如刚进避难所喂女主吃面包那个）\r\n云里雾里的最后结局，补充结局很明显借鉴石头门0\r\n不过我还是挺喜欢女主配音的，很可爱</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_47723661\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"323767\">\n<a href=\"/user/323767\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/32/37/323767.jpg?r=1657351289')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/323767\" class=\"l\">赫特</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars2\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2026-1-12 00:36</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">除了封面图画的还行剩下的的全是史</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_46940790\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"1061718\">\n<a href=\"/user/1061718\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/001/06/17/1061718_81ihn.jpg?r=1764344107&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/1061718\" class=\"l\">砂糖橘ovo</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars3\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2026-1-10 00:48</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">养成系统一坨，分支过多显得很杂乱，ui设计极其灾难，剧情不想评价了，夹杂解密导致支离破碎，te不知道在写什么，只有个别结局勉强能看</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_46859392\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"sakuya214\">\n<a href=\"/user/sakuya214\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/66/82/668223.jpg?r=1718310681&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/sakuya214\" class=\"l\">神剑龙</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars5\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-12-22 00:23</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">橘子班早期模仿作，ED照抄石头门还没抄好，不如原版结局，唯一能说道的就是必须雷普女主才有HE，为什么都爱赛点垃圾小游戏呢</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_46239388\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"950531\">\n<a href=\"/user/950531\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/95/05/950531_9Ownf.jpg?r=1767366667&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/950531\" class=\"l\">皓淇sca</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars5\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-12-3 02:48</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">玩的第一部国g，冗杂的分支以及繁琐的解密和养成系统真的很难不让人红温。剧情还可以吧，真结局的反转很奇妙，卡在了“我超这反转nb”与“这是什么煞笔剧情”之间，有种说不出来的古怪</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_45701395\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"qwq1212546\">\n<a href=\"/user/qwq1212546\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/94/54/945441.jpg?r=1735093159&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/qwq1212546\" class=\"l\">三日月</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars5\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-11-28 01:28</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">当年被截图骗去玩的（）</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_45564576\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"hanying\">\n<a href=\"/user/hanying\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/001/09/90/1099050_qDB3F.jpg?r=1760315969&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/hanying\" class=\"l\">呆萌小苍蝇</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars6\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-11-24 18:02</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">玩得我好力竭，前面一直灌水，虽然说te有点反转但是给我的感觉是就这？</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_45477303\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"sweetbite0v0\">\n<a href=\"/user/sweetbite0v0\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/54/07/540774.jpg?r=1594496930')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/sweetbite0v0\" class=\"l\">冰凉的开水</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars7\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-11-23 14:22</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">现在也印象很深的高中时代作品，记得在那个房间被着窗户光玩，就是最后结局让我有些怅然若失，还看不太懂还去查网</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_45445157\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<template id=\"likes_reaction_grid_item\" type=\"text/template\">\n    <a class=\"item {selected_class}\"\n          href=\"javascript:void(0);\"\n          data-like-type=\"{type}\"\n          data-like-main-id=\"{main_id}\"\n          data-like-related-id=\"{related_id}\"\n          data-like-value=\"{value}\"\n          title=\"{users}\"\n          data-toggle=\"tooltip\">\n        <span class=\"emoji\" style=\"background-image: url('/img/smiles/tv/{emoji}.gif');\"></span>\n        <span class=\"num\">{num}</span>\n    </a>\n</template>\n\n\n<script>\n        var data_likes_list = {\"45701395\":{\"140\":{\"type\":40,\"main_id\":\"196074\",\"value\":\"140\",\"total\":1,\"emoji\":\"101\",\"users\":[{\"username\":\"800793\",\"nickname\":\"blueberryo0.\\u3002\\u8471\"}]}},\"46239388\":{\"104\":{\"type\":40,\"main_id\":\"196074\",\"value\":\"104\",\"total\":1,\"emoji\":\"65\",\"users\":[{\"username\":\"951713\",\"nickname\":\"\\u82e5\\u7d2b\\u4e4b\\u4e0a\"}]}}};\n    </script><a href=\"/subject/196074/